  "description": "1. Create a new node project: `npm init` 2. Install required gulp dependencies:   `npm install gulp-cli --save-dev`   `npm install git+https://github.com/gulpjs/gulp.git#4.0 --save-dev` 3. Install this node module:   `npm install @eightshapes/eightshapes-build-tools --save-dev` 4. Create a `gulpfile.js` in the root of your project. Add the following line:   `const gulp = require('@eightshapes/eightshapes-build-tasks')` 5. Generate the project scaffold:   `gulp generate:project-scaffold` 6. Run the local environment:   `gulp`",
